 was added to make all ‘text templates’ translatable.</p>\n<h2>Configuration</h2>\n<p>A new tab now appears in the WooCommerce Settings that allows you to configure all Woo Deposits settings. From there, the user is able to set the global rules for partial payments, as well as customize the text templates that will appear in the frontend.</p>\n<div id="attachment_435765" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/config1.png"><img class="wp-image-435765 size-medium" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/config1-300x129.png" alt="WooDeposits Configuration" width="300" height="129" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">WooDeposits Configuration</p></div>\n<div id="attachment_435766" style="width: 297px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/config2.png"><img class="wp-image-435766 size-medium" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/config2-287x300.png" alt="WooDeposits Configuration" width="287" height="300" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">WooDeposits Configuration</p></div>\n<div id="attachment_435767" style="width: 230px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/config3.png"><img class="wp-image-435767 size-medium" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/config3-220x300.png" alt="WooDeposits Configuration" width="220" height="300" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">WooDeposits Configuration</p></div>\n<div id="attachment_435768" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/config4.png"><img class="wp-image-435768 size-medium" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/config4-300x100.png" alt="WooDeposits Configuration" width="300" height="100" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">WooDeposits Configuration</p></div>\n<h2>Translating Text Templates</h2>\n<p>All customized text templates strings are automatically registered by WPML and can be translated in WPML&gt;Strings Translation.</p>\n<div id="attachment_435770" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/st-3.png"><img class="wp-image-435770 size-medium" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/st-3-300x158.png" alt="Translating customized text templates" width="300" height="158" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Translating customized text templates</p></div>\n<h2>Frontend</h2>\n<p>The translated strings will appear on the checkout page, and the price will be automatically converted to the current currency.</p>\n<div id="attachment_435772" style="width: 270px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/st2.png"><img class="wp-image-435772 size-medium" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/st2-260x300.png" alt="Cart" width="260" height="300" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Cart</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=k5kd8P8RNXs:xsm9_qv7BJ4:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=k5kd8P8RNXs:xsm9_qv7BJ4:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=k5kd8P8RNXs:xsm9_qv7BJ4:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=k5kd8P8RNXs:xsm9_qv7BJ4:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=k5kd8P8RNXs:xsm9_qv7BJ4:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=k5kd8P8RNXs:xsm9_qv7BJ4:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/k5kd8P8RNXs" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lan